code: import axios from"axios";import config from"../config/config.json";export const getRecordings=async(userId,callback)=>{try{const response=await axios.get("https://".concat(config.hostname,":").concat(config.port,"/api/files/get_recordings/").concat(userId));console.log(response.data);callback(response.data);}catch(e){alert(e);}};
